message.body: img{border:none;} a, a:visited{text-decoration:none;}  .tong{ background:url(../images/images/sy-toubjing_03.gif) repeat-x 0px -11px; width:100%; height:40px;} .wrap{ width:auto; max-width:320px; margin:0 auto;} .center{ width:103%; margin:0 auto;}  /***************分页******************/ .fenye{ float:left; margin-top:10px;} .fenye ul{ float:left; margin-left:32px; } .fenye ul li{ float:left; margin-left:5px;padding: 4px 6px; border:1px solid #ccc;  font-weight:bold; cursor:pointer; color:#999;} .fenye ul li a{ color:#999;} .fenye ul li.xifenye{ width:38px; text-align:center; float:left; position:relative;cursor: pointer;} .fenye ul li .xab{ float:left; position:absolute; width:39px; border:1px solid #ccc; height:123px; overflow-y: auto;overflow-x: hidden;top:-125px; background-color: #fff; display:inline;left:-1px; width:50px;} .fenye ul li .xab ul{ margin-left:0; padding-bottom:0;} .fenye ul li .xab ul li{ border:0; padding:4px 0px; color:#999; width:34px; margin-left:0px; text-align:center;}
